headline: SoftBank Nears Deal for Data Center Investment Firm DigitalBridge
summary: The Japanese conglomerate could announce an agreement as soon as Monday for New York-listed DigitalBridge, the people said, asking not to be identified because the information is private.  Terms of the transaction, part of SoftBank’s campaign to take advantage of an AI-driven boom in digital infrastructure, couldn’t be learned.  Shares in DigitalBridge rose as much as 54% in premarket New York trading Monday.
